            "title": "招金首季淨利按年跌近43%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">招金礦業(01818)公布，截至3 月31日3個月，歸屬母公司股東淨利3.298億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年跌42.94%。每股收益0.08元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"招金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/01818-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"招金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/01818-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">招金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">營業收入7.049億元，按年跌52.96%。營業利潤3.93億元，按年跌40.81%。</p>\n</div>",
